    <item>
      <title>BlackRock，AQR辩论结果ETF增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-31/blackrock-aqr-debate-outcome-etf-growth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BlackRock Inc.预测，到2030年，所谓的以结果为导向的交易所交易资金将三倍至650亿美元的资产。而AQR Capital Management认为，限制股票下跌期间损失的期权驱动的资金带来了较低的回报，而较低的回报则比简单的替代方案更具风险。彭博新闻的Denitsa Tsekova还有更多。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-31/blackrock-aqr-debate-outcome-etf-growth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:44:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
